    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be parting with this absolute beauty, but life\u2019s moving in a new direction. This isn\u2019t just a car; it\u2019s been my pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and polished more often than my shoes! It\u2019s in truly spectacular shape\u2014you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single blemish. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh feeling every time you hop in. I\u2019ve taken care of every little detail so you don't have to. Come by, have a coffee, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of this gem!",
      "price": 48900.0,
